 N1_Situation {
  coords 0 0 0
  m_sTitle "I. SITUATION"
  m_sTextData "<b>a. Enemy Forces</b>"\
  ""\
  "American heavy cavalry troop north west of the river, likely involved in a screening operation that has been preventing the advancing Panzer Regiment 22 from performing deeper reconnaissance."\
  ""\
  "Recent intelligence uncovered the present location of the enemy troop HQ. Further reconnaissance established that its platoons are not currently in the immediate vicinity, but several kilometers to the south west and the north, leaving it vurnerable to unforseen attack."\
  ""\
  "Taking the position would deteriorate the enemy's command and control, cut off any platoons south west of Nyrhilanmaki (facilitating destruction by Panzer Regiment 22), and ultimately allow friendly reconnaissance forces to penetrate the ineffective screen."\
  ""\
  ""\
  "<b>b. Friendly Forces</b>"\
  ""\
  "Company-strength airmobile force of the Luftsturmregiment 40 \"Willi Sänger\", assembled at Metsala Airfield. It consists of 2 platoons with 3 squads each."\
  ""\
  "The force is supported by Mi-24 attack and Mi-8 transport helicopters."\
  ""\
  "The Panzer Regiment 22 \"Soja Kosmodemjanskaja\" is currently advancing north towards the enemy cavalry troop, but will not reach the area until later today."
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "GC_NVA"
  }
  m_iOrder 1
 }
 N2_Mission {
  coords 0 0 0
  m_sTitle "II. MISSION"
  m_sTextData "<b>The company is to conduct an air assault on the enemy troop HQ, SEIZING both Nyrhilanmaki and the western building group within 1 hour.</b>"
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "GC_NVA"
  }
  m_iOrder 2
 }
