  coords 0 0 0
  m_sTitle "III. EXECUTION"
  m_sTextData "<b>Commander's intent</b>"\
  ""\
  "Purpose: Destroy the troop HQ and seize its position in order to cut off enemy forces and prevent them from retreating along the MSR"\
  "Key Tasks:"\
  "- Conduct an air assault on the enemy position"\
  "- Destroy the enemy troop HQ"\
  "- Take control of both marked positions"\
  "End State:"\
  "- Both positions are under control of friendly forces"\
  "- The enemy troop HQ has been largely destroyed"\
  ""\
  ""\
  "<b>Concept of the operation</b>"\
  ""\
